PROJECT: Business Power
BNP Paribas's CLM (Client Lifecycle Management) allows the onboarding of new clients and the updating of
existing client data, with validation of due diligence and support and the support of new regulatory obligations.
This onboarding was used to be done by Relationship Managers (RM) and their Managers (RMM)
through an external application : Salesforce.
Loosing the licence for Salesforce, we got to design and build, an application that:
- is Flexible on the way the data going to be stored
- React to events occuring on the database
- has an embedded, easy to use, Rule Engine
- has to be used by GCARS, a 10 years old legacy application, with ZERO code change
- will be used by Fenergo, a new application currently in deployment in CIB
- is Secure to avoid data corruption
- is easy to Monitor
- has to be available on Mobile
Since its creation, Three use case and application have been onboarded in Business Power: GCARS, COT and
Fenergo
